Definition: a level of material comfort in terms of goods and services available to someone or some group
Example: they enjoyed the highest standard of living in the country; the lower the standard of living the easier it is to introduce an autocratic production system
Synonyms: living_standards, standard_of_life, degree, a, level, of, material, comfort, in, terms, goods, and, services, available, to, someone, or, some, group, they, enjoyed, the, highest, standard, living, country, lower, easier, it, is, introduce, an, autocratic, production, system
Category: noun.state
